<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Moore Campaign — Social Command Center</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0c10;
    --surface: #111318;
    --surface2: #181c24;
    --surface3: #1e2330;
    --border: #252b38;
    --border2: #2e3547;
    --accent: #4f7fff;
    --accent2: #7c5cfc;
    --gold: #e8b84b;
    --red: #ff4f6a;
    --green: #2dd4a0;
    --orange: #ff8c42;
    --text: #e8eaf0;
    --text2: #8892a4;
    --text3: #4e5970;
    --fb: #1877f2;
    --ig: #e1306c;
    --x: #e7e9ea;
    --yt: #ff0000;
    --tt: #69c9d0;
    --radius: 10px;
    --radius-lg: 16px;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; }

  /* PASSWORD GATE */
  #gate {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; background: var(--bg); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; z-index: 999;
    background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% -10%, rgba(79,127,255,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .gate-box { text-align: center; max-width: 380px; width: 90%; }
  .gate-logo { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text2); letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .gate-title { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 2.4rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .gate-sub { color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .gate-input-wrap { position: relative; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .gate-input { width: 100%; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border2); color: var(--text); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 1rem; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: var(--radius); outline: none; letter-spacing: 0.08em; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .gate-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .gate-btn { width: 100%; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: none; padding: 14px; border-radius: var(--radius); font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; letter-spacing: 0.04em; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s; }
  .gate-btn:hover { opacity: 0.88; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .gate-error { color: var(--red); font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 0.6rem; height: 1rem; }
  .gate-hint { color: var(--text3); font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }

  /* MAIN APP */
  #app { display: none; min-height: 100vh; }
  
  /* HEADER */
  header {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10,12,16,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 2rem; height: 58px;
  }
  .header-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .header-logo { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text); }
  .header-logo span { color: var(--accent); }
  .header-badge { background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border2); color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .header-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
  .alert-bell { position: relative; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border2); width: 34px; height: 34px; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .alert-bell:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .alert-bell svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; stroke: var(--text2); }
  .alert-dot { position: absolute; top: 5px; right: 5px; width: 7px; height: 7px; background: var(--red); border-radius: 50%; border: 1.5px solid var(--bg); }
  .live-chip { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--green); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .live-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; background: var(--green); border-radius: 50%; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;} 50%{opacity:0.3;} }

  /* TABS */
  .tab-bar { display: flex; gap: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg); padding: 0 2rem; position: sticky; top: 58px; z-index: 99; }
  .tab { padding: 14px 22px; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text3); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; letter-spacing: 0.04em; transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; white-space: nowrap; }
  .tab:hover { color: var(--text2); }
  .tab.active { color: var(--text); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }
  .tab-icon { margin-right: 6px; }

  /* LAYOUT */
  .page { display: none; padding: 2rem; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page.active { display: block; }

  /* FILTER BAR */
  .filter-bar { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
  .filter-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text3); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-right: 0.25rem; }
  .filter-group { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .filter-btn { background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.15s; font-family: inherit; }
  .filter-btn:hover { border-color: var(--border2); color: var(--text); }
  .filter-btn.active { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
  .filter-divider { width: 1px; background: var(--border); height: 28px; margin: 0 0.25rem; }

  /* STAT CARDS */
  .stats-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .stat-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .stat-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2)); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
  .stat-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .stat-platform { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .platform-icon { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text3); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .stat-value { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.9rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .stat-change { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .stat-change.up { color: var(--green); }
  .stat-change.down { color: var(--red); }

  /* CHARTS */
  .charts-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .chart-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.5rem; }
  .chart-card.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
  .chart-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .chart-title { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .chart-subtitle { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 2px; }
  .chart-canvas-wrap { position: relative; height: 230px; }

  /* TABLES */
  .table-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: hidden; }
  .table-header { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .table-title { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
  .table-sub { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 2px; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  thead th { padding: 10px 1.5rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text3); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface2); }
  tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); transition: background 0.15s; }
  tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  tbody tr:hover { background: var(--surface2); }
  tbody td { padding: 12px 1.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text2); vertical-align: middle; }
  tbody td.strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
  .platform-tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 5px; }
  .platform-tag.fb { background: rgba(24,119,242,0.15); color: var(--fb); }
  .platform-tag.ig { background: rgba(225,48,108,0.15); color: var(--ig); }
  .platform-tag.x  { background: rgba(231,233,234,0.1); color: var(--x); }
  .platform-tag.yt { background: rgba(255,0,0,0.15); color: var(--yt); }
  .platform-tag.tt { background: rgba(105,201,208,0.15); color: var(--tt); }
  .engagement-bar-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .engagement-bar { height: 5px; border-radius: 3px; background: var(--accent); min-width: 4px; transition: width 0.3s; }
  .handle-chip { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; background: var(--surface3); border: 1px solid var(--border2); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text2); }
  .partisan-tag { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .partisan-tag.left { background: rgba(79,127,255,0.15); color: var(--accent); }
  .partisan-tag.right { background: rgba(255,79,106,0.15); color: var(--red); }
  .partisan-tag.center { background: rgba(232,184,75,0.15); color: var(--gold); }
  .partisan-tag.unknown { background: var(--surface3); color: var(--text3); }
  .breakout-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--orange); background: rgba(255,140,66,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(255,140,66,0.25); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .breakout-badge svg { width: 10px; height: 10px; fill: var(--orange); }

  /* COMPETITOR INPUT */
  .competitor-input-bar { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .competitor-input-bar label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text2); letter-spacing: 0.04em; white-space: nowrap; }
  .handle-input { background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border2); color: var(--text); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.82rem; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 7px; outline: none; flex: 1; min-width: 180px; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .handle-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .add-btn { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: none; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 7px; font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .add-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .competitor-chips { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
  .competitor-chip { background: var(--surface3); border: 1px solid var(--border2); color: var(--text2); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .competitor-chip button { background: none; border: none; color: var(--text3); cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1; padding: 0; }
  .competitor-chip button:hover { color: var(--red); }

  /* ALERT PANEL */
  .alert-panel { position: fixed; top: 58px; right: 0; width: 360px; height: calc(100vh - 58px); background: var(--surface); border-left: 1px solid var(--border); z-index: 200; transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform 0.3s ease; overflow-y: auto; }
  .alert-panel.open { transform: translateX(0); }
  .alert-panel-header { padding: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; position: sticky; top: 0; background: var(--surface); }
  .alert-panel-title { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .close-alerts { background: none; border: none; color: var(--text3); cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .alert-item { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); transition: background 0.15s; }
  .alert-item:hover { background: var(--surface2); }
  .alert-item-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .alert-item-platform { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .alert-item-time { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--text3); }
  .alert-item-text { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.45; }
  .alert-item-metric { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--orange); font-weight: 600; margin-top: 4px; }
  .alert-setup { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface2); }
  .alert-setup-label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text3); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .alert-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .alert-form input, .alert-form select { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border2); color: var(--text); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.78rem; padding: 7px 10px; border-radius: 7px; outline: none; width: 100%; }
  .alert-form input:focus, .alert-form select:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .alert-form button { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: none; padding: 8px; border-radius: 7px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .notify-toggle { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .toggle-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text2); flex: 1; }
  .toggle { position: relative; width: 38px; height: 20px; }
  .toggle input { opacity: 0; width: 0; height: 0; }
  .toggle-slider { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: var(--surface3); border-radius: 20px; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .toggle-slider::before { content: ''; position: absolute; width: 14px; height: 14px; left: 3px; top: 3px; background: var(--text3); border-radius: 50%; transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s; }
  .toggle input:checked + .toggle-slider { background: var(--accent); }
  .toggle input:checked + .toggle-slider::before { transform: translateX(18px); background: #fff; }

  /* SECTION HEADINGS */
  .section-label { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text3); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .section-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

  /* EMPTY */
  .empty-state { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem; color: var(--text3); }
  .empty-state svg { width: 40px; height: 40px; margin-bottom: 1rem; stroke: var(--text3); }
  .empty-state p { font-size: 0.85rem; }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .charts-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    header { padding: 0 1rem; }
    .tab-bar { padding: 0 1rem; overflow-x: auto; }
    .page { padding: 1rem; }
    .stats-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  
  /* TOOLTIP custom */
  .tooltip-badge { background: var(--surface3); border: 1px solid var(--border2); color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.68rem; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 4px; }

  .page-intro { color: var(--text3); font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 700px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- PASSWORD GATE -->
<div id="gate">
  <div class="gate-box">
    <div class="gate-logo">Moore Campaign HQ</div>
    <div class="gate-title">Social Command<br/>Center</div>
    <div class="gate-sub">Restricted access. Authorized personnel only.</div>
    <div class="gate-input-wrap">
      <input class="gate-input" id="pwInput" type="password" placeholder="Enter access code" autocomplete="off"/>
    </div>
    <button class="gate-btn" onclick="checkPassword()">Authenticate →</button>
    <div class="gate-error" id="gateError"></div>
    <div class="gate-hint">Demo password: <strong style="color:var(--text2);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;">moore2026</strong></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MAIN APP -->
<div id="app">

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <div class="header-left">
    <div class="header-logo">Moore <span>Command</span></div>
    <div class="header-badge">INTERNAL</div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-right">
    <div class="live-chip"><div class="live-dot"></div> LIVE</div>
    <div class="alert-bell" onclick="toggleAlerts()" title="Breakout Alerts">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"/></svg>
      <div class="alert-dot"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- TAB BAR -->
<div class="tab-bar">
  <div class="tab active" onclick="switchTab(0)"><span class="tab-icon">📊</span>Own Performance</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab(1)"><span class="tab-icon">🔍</span>Social Listening</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab(2)"><span class="tab-icon">⚔️</span>Competitive Analysis</div>
</div>

<!-- ───────────────────── TAB 1: OWN PERFORMANCE ───────────────────── -->
<div class="page active" id="page0">
  <p class="page-intro">Track engagement, follower growth, and top posts across <strong>@govwesmoore</strong> and <strong>@iamwesmoore</strong>.</p>

  <div class="filter-bar">
    <span class="filter-label">Period</span>
    <div class="filter-group" id="periodFilter0">
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setFilter('period0','24h',this)">24h</button>
      <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="setFilter('period0','week',this)">Week</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setFilter('period0','month',this)">Month</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setFilter('period0','year',this)">Year</button>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-divider"></div>
    <span class="filter-label">Handle</span>
    <div class="filter-group" id="handleFilter0">
      <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="setFilter('handle0','all',this)">All</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setFilter('handle0','gov',this)">@govwesmoore</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setFilter('handle0','iam',this)">@iamwesmoore</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STAT CARDS -->
  <div class="stats-row" id="statsRow0"></div>

  <!-- CHARTS -->
  <div class="section-label">Engagement Overview</div>
  <div class="charts-grid">
    <div class="chart-card full">
      <div class="chart-header">
        <div>
          <div class="chart-title">Total Engagement Rate by Platform</div>
          <div class="chart-subtitle">(Likes + Comments) ÷ Followers &nbsp;·&nbsp; Video: Views ÷ Followers</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tooltip-badge">% rate</div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-canvas-wrap"><canvas id="engagementChart"></canvas></div>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-card">
      <div class="chart-header">
        <div>
          <div class="chart-title">Follower Growth</div>
          <div class="chart-subtitle">Net new followers over time</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-canvas-wrap"><canvas id="followerChart"></canvas></div>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-card">
      <div class="chart-header">
        <div>
          <div class="chart-title">Engagement by Content Type</div>
          <div class="chart-subtitle">Text vs. Video performance split</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-canvas-wrap"><canvas id="contentTypeChart"></canvas></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BEST POSTS TABLE -->
  <div class="section-label">Top Posts by Engagement</div>
  <div class="table-card">
    <div class="table-header">
      <div>
        <div class="table-title">Best Performing Posts</div>
        <div class="table-sub">Ranked by engagement rate across all platforms</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="overflow-x:auto;">
      <table id="bestPostsTable">
        <thead><tr>
          <th>Platform</th><th>Handle</th><th>Post Preview</th>
          <th>Likes</th><th>Comments</th><th>Views</th>
          <th>Eng. Rate</th><th>Date</th><th>Status</th>
        </tr></thead>
        <tbody id="bestPostsBody"></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ───────────────────── TAB 2: SOCIAL LISTENING ───────────────────── -->
<div class="page" id="page1">
  <p class="page-intro">Mentions of <strong>Wes Moore</strong>, <strong>Governor Moore</strong>, or <strong>Moore</strong> across Facebook, Instagram, X, YouTube, and TikTok — from accounts <em>other than</em> @govwesmoore and @iamwesmoore.</p>

  <div class="filter-bar">
    <span class="filter-label">Period</span>
    <div class="filter-group">
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setFilter('period1','24h',this)">24h</button>
      <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="setFilter('period1','week',this)">Week</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setFilter('period1','month',this)">Month</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setFilter('period1','year',this)">Year</button>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-divider"></div>
